<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samastaguṇagaṇālaṁkṛta śrīyōgānaṁdanarasiṁ 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>hyadēva divyaśrīpādapadmārādhaka caturvvargapuraṣārttha 
<lb n="3"/>sādhaka duṣṭajanamardda<unclear>na</unclear> śrīnarasiṁhavarddhana nāmādisamastapra 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>śastisahitaṁ śrīmanmahāmaṁḍalēśvara cāgimuppaladēvi 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>Ammaṁgāru svasti śrīśubhaśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1168 Agunēṁ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭi parābhavasaṁvatsara caitraśu 6 Ādivāramu viṣuvusaṁ 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>krāṁtināṁḍu śrītripurāṁtaka śrīmahādēvaraku Akhaṁḍadīpamu 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>na kiccina modavulu 25 vīniṁ jēkoni cennapaseṭṭi penniseṭṭi <unclear>nitya</unclear>māneṁḍu neyi tana (The Inscription stops here Abruptly) <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
</p>

